description:
Katherine couldn’t believe what had happened. And as humiliating as it was,
she was surprised by how much it aroused her. She was guided to a dressing
room to continue her calling. When she enters the room, she’s surprised to
see Kara standing there, waiting for her. She knows this must be part of the
Order’s plan, but she’s so happy to see her the girl she loves.
title: Sister Katherine: Unveiling
